FT  25 JUN 92 / Moldovans warned on TransDnestr air attacks: Russian 14th
army officials say aggressive aircraft will be shot down on sight
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By CHRYSTIA FREELAND
</BYLINE>
